{"tid":611493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★鴻海季度盈利大超預期　反映iPhone X需求旺盛","createTime":"2018-03-31T05:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T06:24:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"805e97fa90a26d1a0450638d1ad5942775004142","tid":611493,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)主要代工的富智康母公司鴻海集團公布，去年第四季，淨利潤錄717億元新台幣(約193億港元)，大幅超過市場預期的580億元新台幣；收入則錄1.73萬億元新台幣的紀錄最高。<br />\n<br />\n鴻海超過一半的收入來自蘋果，期內業績做好，相信主要得益於市場對Apple iPhone X的旺盛需求。除了蘋果公司的收入外，鴻海總裁郭台銘亦正在尋找其他方式來擴大業務，而不僅局限於組裝零部件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180331/bkn-20180331043827711-0331_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180331%2Fbkn-20180331043827711-0331_00842_001.html&d=4%2BrRIQTk%2BJ4g0iBcleXrgWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c2ca206c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180331/bkn-20180331043827711-0331_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7ba739377765f192550d465fa0c6a7b272bf727c","tid":611493,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"why????<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2930741b91d25f6825699cefbce9d9cc2e787e","tid":611493,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/apUIqBEnmYk/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FapUIqBEnmYk%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=eab88acc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bf593efc02122d5bed6781b35b3e03e660e02a4","tid":611493,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"邊個話冇人買X <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}